Description
-----------

This CVar allows for the third person perspective camera to be used
while the player is dead.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    pm_thirdPersonDeath [bool]

Parameters
----------

-   [bool] - Enables/Disables the the third person perspective camera
    while the player is dead.
    -   0 - Turns this feature off.
    -   1 - Turns this feature on.

